## ğŸ¯ Using EyeCare

### Display Settings

![Display Settings](Screenshot_2026-02-08_184720.png)

- **Adjust Warmth** (color temperature) â€” slide from Warm to Cool
- **Adjust Brightness** â€” slide from Dimmer to Brighter
- **Presets**: Health, Office, Reading, Game, Movie, Editing, Custom
- **Day/Night Toggle**:
  - "Day" sets light mode + bright preset
  - "Night" sets dark mode + warmer preset
- **Activate**: Click "Enable Filter" to turn on the screen overlay filter

### Schedule

![Schedule Settings](Screenshot_2026-02-08_184731.png)

- **Automatic Schedule**: Enable filter during evening hours to reduce eye strain
- **Schedule Settings**:
  - Set when to enable filter (default: 20:00)
  - Set when to disable filter (default: 06:00)
- **Transition Style**:
  - Gradual â€” smooth 30-minute transition
  - Instant â€” apply immediately
- **Active Days**: Select which days the schedule should run

### Settings

![General Settings](Screenshot_2026-02-08_184751.png)

**General Preferences:**
- Launch at Startup â€” automatically start EyeCare when you log in
- Minimize to System Tray â€” keep app running in background when closed
- Show Notifications â€” display system notifications for events

