## ğŸ—‘ï¸ Uninstall

**Installed via EXE:**
- Open **Add or remove programs** (Settings â†’ Apps)
- Find **EyeCare** and click Uninstall

**Portable ZIP:**
- Close the app and delete the folder

---

## ğŸ”§ Troubleshooting

**Overlay not visible:**
- Press `Ctrl + Alt + F` to toggle
- Ensure no other overlay apps are running

**Styles look plain:**
- Restart the app; ensure you downloaded the latest release

**Antivirus warnings:**
- The app is packaged with Electron; allow it if flagged

**App won't launch:**
- Reboot Windows, then reinstall the latest release

---

## ğŸ”’ Privacy & Permissions

- EyeCare does not collect or transmit personal data
- No special permissions are required; overlay runs on top of the screen only

